{"tid":2118663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"收成波已報名爭連任，得134票嘅保險界仲有幾多張10票提名比牙作入閘？","createTime":"2020-07-21T14:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T04:09:47.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"312d7b5844ebbc255b8adbe771b2c5abca7fee73","tid":2118663,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2020/pdf/FC_ALLO_c.pdf?time=0.0566220546152969.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Flegco2020%2Fpdf%2FFC_ALLO_c.pdf%3Ftime%3D0.0566220546152969.pdf&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=c3258693\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2020/pdf/FC_ALLO_c.pdf?time=0.0566220546152969.pdf</a><br />\n<blockquote>保險界 陳健波 男 立法會議員 2020年7月21日</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/05/Rwht3m.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20080313064940\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F05%2FRwht3m.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20080313064940&h=c91b71af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>已登記為選民的數目<br />\n航運交通界 191<br />\n鄉議局 155<br />\n漁農界 152<br />\n<span class=\"red\">保險界 134</span><br />\n金融界 121<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/statistic20203.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fstatistic20203.html&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=cce28360\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/statistic20203.html</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩，仲有114票比你R<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/5a/7dayshiromi.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20080315070019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F5a%2F7dayshiromi.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20080315070019&h=27acef07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>(ii) 就 傳 統 功 能 界 別 的 候 選 人 而 言 ， 提 名 部 分 必 須 由 10 名 已 登 記 選 ⺠ (候 選 人 以 外 者 )簽署 ， 而 可 在 某 份 提 名 表 格 上 簽署 為 提 名 人的 人 數 <span class=\"red\">不 得 超 過 20 名 </span></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/pdf/legco/2020lc_guide/ch/chapter_4.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fpdf%2Flegco%2F2020lc_guide%2Fch%2Fchapter_4.pdf&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=2de8a60f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/pdf/legco/2020lc_guide/ch/chapter_4.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ed56101348f2c1767214c958341217d0d7cac350","tid":2118663,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idxQdn5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidxQdn5.png&h=de142aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5a7610e8fa9ce09db44cb38eaf448942d60baa","tid":2118663,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"「我會將踢走保險狗寫入本人參選政綱。我為人正直，提供專業服務獲得理想回報然後投資西裝置裝。你地死sell親朋戚友、斷六親成死sales冇數然後拼死污衊保險界明日之星（其實已經係今日）。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9002b1f47b8488d9b2df65ccaefe3f738d73d22","tid":2118663,"uid":100570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"屌你果兩張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3f70bd741822c7b7317da319121bd868668646","tid":2118663,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"旅遊界1,486票 10票提名都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅遊界有手足可能入唔到閘啊！！旅遊界選民快D幫幫手啊！！<br />\n- 分享自 